  <brief_title>Weekly Docetaxel Plus Cisplatin or Oxaliplatin for AGC</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Phase II Trial of Weekly Docetaxel/Cisplatin Versus Weekly Docetaxel/Oxaliplatin in Previously Untreated Patients With Advanced Gastric Cancer</official_title>
